  "status": "active",
  "version": 1,
  "summary": "Use only three styles of Callout Formatting: Main callout with bold Brand Blue (#00529b) text, Gold (#ffc60a) 2px horizontal rules (60\u2013100% width, 16px padding); Secondary callout light Blue (#E6F0F9) 70% tint box, bold Brand Blue text, 20px padding, corner radius; Text-heavy callout Golden Sand (#FEF1C8) 30% tint box, bold Brand Blue headline, bold Sky Blue (#358CCB) subheads, graphite body, 24px padding, two-column layout collapses on mobile."
